member.name: M:FMEA.Engine.CEngine.StressAndConditionGeneration(System.Int32,System.Collections.Generic.List{FMEA.Engine.CElementAnalysed},FMEA.Configuration.IConfiguration)
member.summary: For one iterration, for each element, uses the stresses and conditions associated with that element and determines what processes will be launched. Stores the results in the associated ElementAnalysed object.
